==Portuguese==

===Etymology===
Latin ''[[multus]]''

===Pronunciation===
/ˈmũj̃tu/

===Adjective===
'''muito''' ''m sing'', '''muitos''' ''m plural'', '''muita''' ''f sing'', '''muitas''' ''f plural''

# [[much]], [[many]], [[a lot]]/lots of
: ''Tenho muitas coisas para fazer.'' I have many things to do.

===Adverb===
'''muito''' ''adv''

# [[very]], [[much]], very much
: ''Gosto muito de você.'' I like you very much.

